### Get environment for an app

```
Definition
```

```http
GET /v3/apps/:guid/env HTTP/1.1
```

```
Example Request
```

```shell
curl "https://api.example.org/v3/apps/[guid]/env" \
  -X GET \
  -H "Authorization: bearer [token]"
```

```
Example Response
```

```http
